@startuml
[*] as InitialState
ScreenState as State
LoginScreenState as LoginState
UploadDocumentState as UploadDocState
ApplyForCertificateState as ApplyCertState
ReapplyForCertificateState as ReapplyCertState
RequestVerificationState as RequestVerifState
EndSessionState as EndSession

InitialState ->> State: User enters details
State ->> LoginState: Correct login credentials entered
LoginState ->> UploadDocState: User selects "Upload Documents"
LoginState ->> ApplyCertState: User selects "Apply for Certificate"
UploadDocState ->> UploadDocState: User continues uploading documents
ApplyCertState ->> ReapplyCertState: User applies for multiple certificates or reapplying after sending request
ReapplyCertState ->> RequestVerifState: User sends request to issuer
RequestVerifState ->> EndSessionState: Issuer verifies and notifies user
UploadDocState ->> LoginState: User logs out and logs back in
ApplyCertState ->> LoginState: User logs out and logs back in

LoginState ->> EndSessionState: Incorrect login credentials entered or user logs out
EndSessionState as FinalState

[*] --> InitialState: System restarts
InitialState --> State: User enters details for first time registration

@enduml
